Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,了不起的鬼平在感冒面前也会倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 烧已经退了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你要卧床休息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,立泉大夫让你好好静养
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,得病也是福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.74,0:00:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么需要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-她走了吧？\N-走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好 快拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好酒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,偷偷喝酒感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好东西不只有美酒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-我可少不得这个\N-也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看你抽烟真是很享受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,烟草放在这个烟管里味道更好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.53,0:01:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它有什么特别吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.25,0:01:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这支可随身携带的银烟管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是烟管大师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,后藤左卫门所制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是家父当年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在京都当差时请他做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不是贵重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但你看它这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,拔钉钳家徽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,总之家父为这个银烟管花了15两呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是令尊的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到您这么久还没康复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉久荣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天和左马之助小酌了几杯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以病情才会反复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天休息一天就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我处理公务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不必客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么时候开始变得这么脆弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一场感冒居然把我弄成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-天哪\N-早上的感觉好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你和昨天判若两人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,您要当心身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,立泉大夫希望你能休养三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是卧床三个月 就该发霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,和发霉的丈夫睡在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会被传染发霉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这种话别说这么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 久荣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么事？\N-我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我想抽一管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说抽烟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是 不然还能是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,立泉大夫严令禁止你抽烟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,长谷川平藏的夫人\N怎么这么不通情理？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你要答应我只抽一管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,公公的烟管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细找找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我清楚记得昨晚睡前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,把它收好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？快找找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再仔细找一找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-好了\N-什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,久荣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别声张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你想到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,若我想得没错 事情就严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这说明盗贼闯入了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,火付盗贼改方官员的府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你要出门？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我该出门巡视一番了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你陪我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我怕感冒复发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 老铁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们为你的康复 出去庆祝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我指的就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你不起好作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去喝一杯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我等你这话好久了 老铁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那个叫加贺屋的舟宿怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你去过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这样更有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,能去欣赏河景也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们第一次来\N-欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老铁 不会有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,船夫年纪不小了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来像烤蔫了的鱼糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,左马之助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这位船夫就算遇到龙卷风都面不改色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,您尊姓大名可否告知？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老夫叫友五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在下岸井左马太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,记住我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,以后我会常来光顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,能在那边停下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-我母亲的亲戚住在那里\N-好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-多谢\N-慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 老板？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了 这件事只能你知我知
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在紫安桥附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有个叫加贺屋的舟宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那里有一个船夫 名叫友五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你去探探他的底细
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,别被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你要出去调查？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,（加贺舟宿）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想乘船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,听说这里有位技术不错的船夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老人家 我能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我脸上沾了什么东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是你吗 粂八？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到会在这里见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起当大盗已经是十年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,以前当大盗 现在我在这里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里当船夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不叫滨崎友藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在是良民友五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,友五郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不做贼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在在谁手下做事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 自从血头丹兵卫的头目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,三年前被火付盗贼改方抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我就没有固定的东家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你到处流窜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但最近江户地区不好下手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定也听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,只要火付盗贼改方的长官鬼平在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,根本没法下手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,若是从前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,根本不把那个鬼平放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是如今 我也不怕他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,粂八
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我们是老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我就告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我赢过鬼平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,太多人对他歌功颂德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,让我盗贼之心躁动不安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,上周 我溜进来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,火付盗贼改方的府邸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么时候开始变得这么脆弱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一场感冒居然把我弄成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,证据在此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,鬼平？别被他的名字吓破胆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他当时睡了 根本没发现我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如今的盗贼都胆小如鼠\N才显得他厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你看清鬼平的脸了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没看清 当时屋里很暗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,粂八 老朽68岁 都能做这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你何不在江户中心干一票大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,让鬼平开开眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你都干了什么 老爹？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到真有盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,敢到火付盗贼改方的官舍作案
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,说明这里的官员都睡得很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,对于滨崎友藏而言…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对于友五郎而言 这太容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他也令我鬼平丢了颜面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真的要缉拿他吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,即使只偷一支烟管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,盗贼就是盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你想求我放过他？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝杯酒考虑考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么精彩的故事要告诉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-老爹 我也溜进去了\N-什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你偷偷潜入时\N官舍一定破绽百出 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可自从你偷了鬼平的银烟管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那里的戒备就更加森严了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我小房粂八\N不会像你一样一等就是十年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我没退出盗贼这一行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不能轻易放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我决定冒险一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？你不信的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看到没？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹 我知道你心痒难耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你见识一下 我会再次潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,戒备森严的火付盗贼改方官舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这样如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也再进去一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把官印盒放回柜子里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹 你把烟管放进柜子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,再偷这个官印盒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-若你能成功…\N-怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我粂八就给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,30两金子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我从不说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你何时去还官印盒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣吧 老爹？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这对老搭档今晚就大闹鬼平府
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好 放在柜子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,长谷川大人 拜托您不要伤害老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会提起你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,粂八最近常来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在调查什么特别的案件吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你也应该知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,粂八在和我玩个游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-他今晚会来\N-好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他会不会来看我的脸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚有窃贼闯入 盗走我卧室的印盒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,若被百姓知晓…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 若被其他盗贼知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将颜面扫地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,成为众人的笑柄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,包括我在内的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,从今往后 要高度警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,严守岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,再发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我长谷川平藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,会立即辞去职务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-是\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,居然有人敢偷我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很好笑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看我们失职 你开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就连头儿也疏忽了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,贼闯进卧室 他还在呼呼大睡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,（加贺舟宿）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,您是岸井先生吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,您还记得我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,心情大好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,龟鹤相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有好事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,认识年轻姑娘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我都快70岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就像春天的朦胧月光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,客官 你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,明天会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮这么明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,河里的隐居者比月亮靠得住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,河里的隐居者？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,它来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 隐居者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,隐居者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很硬朗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,客官 隐居者在这条河里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,生活了70多年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我小时候就认识它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,它能分辨渔夫的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我来它就会现身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,后会有期 隐居者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这条锦鲤真是庞然大物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你让我大开眼界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一起喝一杯吧 让我表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你倒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可以？谢谢客官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,马上有佳肴呈上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我们慢慢喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,头一次见你这种性情温厚的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你是有钱的浪人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想听听老爷子你的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我这一生没什么大作为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,收下这一两 把印盒还给我 行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,烟管和印盒都是家父的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我视如珍宝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,（下集预告）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,平藏命中注定的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.13,0:23:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,男人是他难忘的恩师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.34,0:23:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,下集再见
